{"tid":769443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[tvb不會報導系列]羽毛球世錦賽 日本國旗在南京升起　支那網友崩潰了 |","createTime":"2018-08-06T07:30:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-09T01:31:44.000Z","uid":54373,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"0aefbd25bd760561d41d7d172ba289d40b937ee0","tid":769443,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T07:30:05.000Z","msg":"▲頒獎典禮時，升起了三面日本國旗，讓許多大陸網友崩潰了。（圖／翻攝自微博）<br />\n<br />\n2018年羽球世錦賽在中國大陸南京舉辦，今年的羽球女雙，冠亞軍都是由日本隊包下。在舉行頒獎典禮，現場奏起了日本國歌並升起了三面日本國旗，沒想到此舉卻讓中國大陸的網友都崩潰了。"},{"pid":"0de2077bd5b2e3834fa7b1614cd8a38b92aa4fd0","tid":769443,"uid":54373,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T07:32:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imagelab.nownews.com/?w=1080&amp;q=85&amp;src=https://rssimg.nownews.com/images/5b67f7994eeeb54b135a6771_201808061524.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimagelab.nownews.com%2F%3Fw%3D1080%26q%3D85%26src%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Frssimg.nownews.com%2Fimages%2F5b67f7994eeeb54b135a6771_201808061524.jpg&h=abe48d0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲頒獎典禮時，升起了三面日本國旗，讓許多大陸網友崩潰了。（圖／翻攝自微博）"},{"pid":"8e0de95ec385b39ac848919af7e79d36970c0ab0","tid":769443,"uid":5218,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T07:32:44.000Z","msg":"大陸閪郁 d 都崩潰咖啦，都廢既。"},{"pid":"e318e6cda830c2cde1321532401b9a3a81934ae8","tid":769443,"uid":156005,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T07:35:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁人地真係贏到呀，吹咩"},{"pid":"e3287c06d9ff594091d084c8f33cfbd9f8cd5332","tid":769443,"uid":33808,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T07:37:13.000Z","msg":"報喜不報憂，之前勁嗰陣就瘋狂報，失意就唔提。培養出自大，接受唔到失敗嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n又，南京事隔多年，拎獎嘅呢批同當年日軍都唔同嘅人來，相比當年日軍，中共到今日仲屠害緊更多人，都唔知有咩咩更崩潰過呢樣。"},{"pid":"ee9bbdac13f8f6b0e59eff7dc7f47d289930e218","tid":769443,"uid":1221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T07:37:43.000Z","msg":"碎到一地都係"},{"pid":"4b6271ada55ec17fd04e407a6ae86bacd03a2030","tid":769443,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T07:38:43.000Z","msg":"想睇留言"},{"pid":"ab5201a096cf90950867d2da634780584dff854e","tid":769443,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T07:38:48.000Z","msg":"技不如人崩咩潰"},{"pid":"a936cb907e6db24de9042ed88ea50081770a683a","tid":769443,"uid":23635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T07:39:52.000Z","msg":"仲有男單都係日本金牌，女單強國直頭四強都冇人入到"},{"pid":"f5beaeff0aedf0b0315d1d89f997600982ff115a","tid":769443,"uid":2054,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T07:39:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a7f37f122959a2f90f7c78b06e6ca8c920543a7","tid":769443,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a936cb907e6db24de9042ed88ea50081770a683a","tid":769443,"uid":23635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T07:39:52.000Z","msg":"仲有男單都係日本金牌，女單強國直頭四強都冇人入到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T07:40:29.000Z","msg":"林丹呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0c9e48c5ddeb2e83313db160a047fa30fdb4ecd","tid":769443,"uid":87780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T07:40:32.000Z","msg":"咁小家就咪撚搞比賽囉"},{"pid":"447783f88124ffa8fa0ff82c364cfd674c